10. Representation and Use of Domain Nam:
{
    "10. Representation and Use of Domain Names": [
        {
            "Original": "So that domain names may be encoded uniformly, a domain name or a list of domain names is encoded using the technique described in[Section 3.1 of [RFC1035]](https://www.rfc-editor.org/rfc/rfc1035#section-3.1).",
